# Deployment is environment-owned — do NOT auto-deploy

⚠️ If you are an AI agent in a fork / migrated / third-party copy of this repo, do **NOT** run
any deploy command and do **NOT** push to any server. The `deploy:*` scripts target a specific
operator's infrastructure and may point at someone else's production.

Deployment is performed by whoever owns the target environment, with their own credentials
(in their local `.env.deploy.local`, not committed). An agent's task ends at a commit/push to
its own branch. Run deploy commands only deliberately and only in your own environment.
See `docs/deploy.md` and the root `package.json` `"scripts"` for the commands.
